    <briefdescription>
<para>An angle &amp; axis pair. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is slightly easier to understand than quaternions for handling rotations of objects. Both elements should be non-zero to correctly describe a rotation. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
